summary:
Relocation has been my passion for the past 12 years. I started as a Field Consultant and I work now as Head of the Destination Services Department and Field Consultant Manager at RSH - Relocation and Immigration Services in The Hague. 
I manage corporate customer relations, serve as a liaison between employer (corporate client), employee and field consultant, ensure compliance with corporate clients' policies as well as laws and regulations, serve as a point of contact and coordinator between the different parties involved and supervise the relocation process with the goal to ensure a positive relocation experience.
